1
00:00:36,564 --> 00:00:39,651
MAC 2007, MUSIM BUNGA KE LAPAN BELAS

2
00:00:39,734 --> 00:00:40,735
Jom.

3
00:00:42,070 --> 00:00:44,114
Hai, semua!

4
00:00:44,197 --> 00:00:45,156
- Awak pun di sini?
- Sama kelas?

5
00:00:45,740 --> 00:00:47,075
Kamu ikut saya?

6
00:00:47,158 --> 00:00:49,619
Tak ada muka barukah? Apa ini?

7
00:00:50,119 --> 00:00:51,329
Bosan betul.

8
00:00:51,412 --> 00:00:54,374
Saya lebih terkejut
awak masuk aliran sains.

9
00:00:55,333 --> 00:00:57,502
Awak nak rendahkan
purata markah Matematik?

10
00:00:57,585 --> 00:00:59,838
Su-jin, sudahlah. Kita sekelas.

11
00:01:07,637 --> 00:01:10,056
Tak boleh. Tempat ini dah bertuan.

12
00:01:10,140 --> 00:01:11,808
Siapa? Awak?

13
00:01:13,518 --> 00:01:15,478
Tak. Bukan saya…

14
00:01:15,562 --> 00:01:17,188
Ke tepi.

15
00:01:17,272 --> 00:01:18,898
Pencahayaan di sini bagus,

16
00:01:19,858 --> 00:01:21,401
saya nampak sangat kacak.

17
00:01:22,110 --> 00:01:23,862
Bukan sebab pencahayaan,

18
00:01:23,945 --> 00:01:26,156
tapi sebab Heon yang kacak duduk di sini.

19
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,407
Awak terlalu kusam.

20
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:28,950
Tak ada cahaya yang boleh bantu.

21
00:01:29,033 --> 00:01:30,410
"Kusam"?

22
00:01:31,119 --> 00:01:32,328
Heon!

23
00:01:41,963 --> 00:01:43,381
Selamat pagi.

24
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,676
Ha-young, sakitlah.

25
00:01:47,427 --> 00:01:50,138
Sol-i, awak berjaya pastikan
dia duduk di sebelah awak.

26
00:01:50,638 --> 00:01:52,599
Loceng dah berbunyi. Duduklah.

27
00:01:53,516 --> 00:01:56,060
Kenapa dia masih berlagak
seperti ketua kelas?

28
00:01:56,144 --> 00:01:58,646
Itulah dan kenapa dia
masih sekelas dengan kita?

29
00:01:58,730 --> 00:02:00,732
- Hai, semua!
- Dae-sung, hai.

30
00:02:00,815 --> 00:02:02,317
- Aduhai.
- Hai.

31
00:02:07,655 --> 00:02:10,158
Apa khabar, semua?

32
00:02:12,702 --> 00:02:15,288
Cikgu akan jadi guru kelas kamu semua.

33
00:02:15,872 --> 00:02:19,959
Walaupun ini kelas aliran sains,
awak tak boleh abaikan sastera.

34
00:02:20,043 --> 00:02:21,294
- Baiklah!
- Baiklah!

35
00:02:21,377 --> 00:02:23,630
Mari kita buat yang terbaik!

36
00:02:29,594 --> 00:02:32,597
CARL SAGAN
<i>COSMOS</i>

37
00:02:44,442 --> 00:02:45,485
<i>Cosmos</i>?

38
00:02:46,402 --> 00:02:47,570
Awak suka bunga?

39
00:02:47,654 --> 00:02:49,280
Buku ini tentang alam semesta.

40
00:02:50,740 --> 00:02:54,160
Tapi tajuk buku itu sangat cantik.
Sama seperti awak.

41
00:02:54,243 --> 00:02:56,037
Awak mengganggu saya. Pergi.

42
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:58,665
Tak, buku ini yang mengganggu
pandangan saya.

43
00:02:58,748 --> 00:03:00,458
Kita patut hapuskan buku ini.

44
00:03:01,584 --> 00:03:02,418
Hei!

45
00:03:03,294 --> 00:03:04,545
- Pulangkan.
- Tak nak.

46
00:03:05,046 --> 00:03:06,631
- Helo.
- Hai.

47
00:03:07,215 --> 00:03:08,591
Helo.

48
00:03:08,675 --> 00:03:11,552
Ha-young. Awak sihat?

49
00:03:12,136 --> 00:03:13,388
Ya, sudah tentu.

50
00:03:13,471 --> 00:03:15,640
Hati-hati dan jangan berlari.

51
00:03:15,723 --> 00:03:17,350
Baiklah.

52
00:03:23,856 --> 00:03:25,525
Ha-young, dah selesai?

53
00:03:26,401 --> 00:03:27,610
Saya akan lari semula.

54
00:03:27,694 --> 00:03:29,696
Kejarlah saya.

55
00:03:29,779 --> 00:03:31,948
Dungu betul. Apa dia buat ini?

56
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:34,701
Hei!

57
00:03:37,245 --> 00:03:38,413
Jangan berlari.

58
00:03:41,207 --> 00:03:42,667
Penuh berkuasa.

59
00:03:43,334 --> 00:03:44,502
Ha-young!

60
00:03:51,134 --> 00:03:52,510
Tengok!

61
00:03:53,011 --> 00:03:55,138
Itu pertandingan "<i>Korea</i>…"

62
00:03:55,221 --> 00:03:56,597
- "<i>Sings</i>!"
- "<i>Sings</i>!"

63
00:04:04,063 --> 00:04:05,565
Awak nak ambil bahagian?

64
00:04:05,648 --> 00:04:07,692
Ya, Sabtu ini. Jom pergi sama.

65
00:04:07,775 --> 00:04:09,235
Kamu boleh beri sokongan.

66
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,903
Saya tak boleh pergi. Jauh.

67
00:04:10,987 --> 00:04:12,530
Ha-young…

68
00:04:13,114 --> 00:04:15,283
Ia dah lama tak diadakan di Gyeonggi-do.

69
00:04:15,366 --> 00:04:17,368
Lagipun, Osan tak jauh.

70
00:04:17,452 --> 00:04:19,329
Sejam saja dengan bas.

71
00:04:19,412 --> 00:04:21,247
Yakah? Begitu dekat?

72
00:04:21,331 --> 00:04:24,292
Ya, tapi perlu bertukar bas
sebanyak tiga kali.

73
00:04:26,294 --> 00:04:29,172
Saya akan tunjukkan bakat tersembunyi
dan jadi bintang terkenal.

74
00:04:29,255 --> 00:04:31,632
Tentu mereka berebut
untuk jadikan saya idola.

75
00:04:31,716 --> 00:04:33,801
Aduhai, besarnya impian awak.

76
00:04:34,385 --> 00:04:36,429
Betul, tak salah untuk bermimpi.

77
00:04:36,512 --> 00:04:39,766
Apa yang awak tahu?
Awak cuma tahu berenang saja.

78
00:04:39,849 --> 00:04:42,477
Kamu semua akan pergi sama, bukan?

79
00:04:45,521 --> 00:04:47,398
Saya nak ikut. Tentu seronok.

80
00:04:47,482 --> 00:04:49,025
Okey!

81
00:04:49,817 --> 00:04:52,487
Awak dah lulus uji bakat?

82
00:04:53,988 --> 00:04:55,156
Belum.

83
00:05:04,165 --> 00:05:05,625
- Bila?
- Sabtu ini.

84
00:05:05,708 --> 00:05:07,210
- Sabtu? Okey.
- Okey.

85
00:05:07,752 --> 00:05:10,171
- Awak!
- Letak dulu tulang itu.

86
00:05:10,254 --> 00:05:11,798
Ia nampak bahaya.

87
00:05:11,881 --> 00:05:13,466
Mak, Sabtu ini, saya…

88
00:05:13,549 --> 00:05:16,260
Pastikan awak minta semula duit itu esok.

89
00:05:16,344 --> 00:05:18,304
Kalau tak, saya akan mengamuk.

90
00:05:18,388 --> 00:05:23,017
Sebenarnya, Ji-sun dah ke Macao hari ini
atas urusan kerja.

91
00:05:23,101 --> 00:05:25,144
Apa? Ji-sun tak guna itu?

92
00:05:25,228 --> 00:05:27,980
Hei, Shin Gi-heon! Awak…

93
00:05:32,610 --> 00:05:33,861
Apa ini?

94
00:05:33,945 --> 00:05:36,697
Awak lempar daging
ke muka saya yang kacak ini?

95
00:05:36,781 --> 00:05:38,991
Saya tak nak dengar apa-apa lagi. Keluar.

96
00:05:39,075 --> 00:05:40,368
Keluar sekarang juga!

97
00:05:40,451 --> 00:05:43,037
Itu duit saya. Kenapa saya kena marah?

98
00:05:43,121 --> 00:05:45,540
Duit awak? Itu duit poket yang saya beri.

99
00:05:45,623 --> 00:05:47,291
Saya dah tak sanggup…

100
00:05:48,918 --> 00:05:51,337
hidup dilayan begini lagi!

101
00:05:52,547 --> 00:05:53,714
Ayah…

102
00:05:56,801 --> 00:05:59,095
Baiklah. Saya dah tak tahan juga!

103
00:06:01,514 --> 00:06:02,557
Mak…

104
00:06:07,603 --> 00:06:10,064
Maaf, tapi angin saya tak begitu baik.

105
00:06:10,148 --> 00:06:13,234
Saya perlukan kamu semua
untuk beri semangat. Duduk.

106
00:06:21,576 --> 00:06:22,410
Helo?

107
00:06:22,493 --> 00:06:26,372
Ya. Saya peserta nombor 178,
Jeong Jin-hwan!

108
00:06:27,748 --> 00:06:29,792
Boleh saya mulakan sekarang? Baiklah!

109
00:06:41,512 --> 00:06:44,223
<i>Maaf. Mulakan daripada korus.</i>

110
00:06:44,307 --> 00:06:46,601
Bahagian korus? Baiklah.

111
00:06:46,684 --> 00:06:48,603
Saya mulakan sekali lagi.

112
00:06:50,354 --> 00:06:53,774
<i>Inilah cinta</i>

113
00:06:53,858 --> 00:06:57,361
<i>Walau terpadam, ia tetap cinta</i>

114
00:06:57,445 --> 00:07:01,199
<i>Aku cuba lepaskanmu</i>

115
00:07:01,282 --> 00:07:04,660
<i>Namun hanya kamulah di hatiku</i>

116
00:07:04,744 --> 00:07:08,372
<i>Hanya kamu</i>

117
00:07:08,456 --> 00:07:12,126
<i>Kamulah yang aku mahu</i>

118
00:07:12,210 --> 00:07:15,963
<i>Aku rakam gambarmu</i>

119
00:07:16,547 --> 00:07:21,594
<i>Buat tatapan di kamarku</i>

120
00:07:21,677 --> 00:07:23,554
<i>Awak lulus uji bakat pertama.</i>

121
00:07:28,601 --> 00:07:31,562
Terima kasih! Terima kasih banyak.

122
00:07:34,774 --> 00:07:36,234
Saya lulus!

123
00:07:36,984 --> 00:07:40,238
Kawan-kawan, saya akan debut.

124
00:07:40,321 --> 00:07:43,241
Perlukah awak ke Osan
untuk uji bakat kedua?

125
00:07:43,324 --> 00:07:44,283
Tentulah.

126
00:07:44,367 --> 00:07:47,537
Ha-young, saya akan
laungkan nama awak di TV.

127
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:50,122
Kamu semua akan pergi sama, bukan?

128
00:07:50,706 --> 00:07:54,001
Saya tak pasti saya boleh pergi.

129
00:07:54,877 --> 00:07:56,879
Kalau itu jawapan Sol-i,

130
00:07:57,797 --> 00:07:59,715
saya tak boleh janji juga.

131
00:07:59,799 --> 00:08:02,343
Sol-i, awak wajib pergi. Apa ini?

132
00:08:05,638 --> 00:08:07,598
Saya dah balik.

133
00:08:18,568 --> 00:08:20,194
<i>Mak ke luar bandar.</i>

134
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:22,613
<i>Tak usah tunggu. Tidur dulu.</i>

135
00:08:44,594 --> 00:08:45,803
Awak buat apa?

136
00:08:48,014 --> 00:08:49,056
Heon…

137
00:08:54,937 --> 00:08:56,105
Kenapa ini?

138
00:08:58,649 --> 00:08:59,900
Apa patut saya buat?

139
00:09:00,568 --> 00:09:02,862
Mak dan ayah saya bertengkar

140
00:09:02,945 --> 00:09:05,740
dan dah dua hari ayah saya tak pulang.

141
00:09:07,742 --> 00:09:10,536
Saya cuma hubungi ayah, tapi tak berjaya.

142
00:09:11,579 --> 00:09:13,998
Tadi saya pulang
dan mak saya tak ada juga.

143
00:09:16,208 --> 00:09:19,545
Kalau mak dan ayah saya bercerai,

144
00:09:20,129 --> 00:09:21,756
macam mana dengan saya?

145
00:09:27,845 --> 00:09:28,846
Hei…

146
00:09:37,647 --> 00:09:38,898
Okey.

147
00:09:55,206 --> 00:09:57,208
Yang itu dah basah.

148
00:10:16,602 --> 00:10:19,563
<i>Semuanya pasti okey. Jangan risau.</i>

149
00:10:19,647 --> 00:10:22,191
TULIS MESEJ
SHIN SOL-I

150
00:10:22,274 --> 00:10:23,943
HANTAR

151
00:10:24,026 --> 00:10:26,028
HANTAR MESEJ? YA ATAU BATAL.

152
00:10:32,368 --> 00:10:33,285
Abang!

153
00:10:33,369 --> 00:10:34,453
HANTAR MESEJ

154
00:10:36,288 --> 00:10:38,207
Abang, mak minta baju kotor.

155
00:10:41,377 --> 00:10:43,170
Atas itu. Ambillah.

156
00:10:51,262 --> 00:10:54,557
Tapi kenapa lengan baju ini basah?

157
00:10:57,893 --> 00:10:59,395
Ada anjing jilat.

158
00:10:59,478 --> 00:11:01,272
Di sini ada anjing?

159
00:11:01,355 --> 00:11:03,941
Saya tak pernah nampak. Comel tak?

160
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:09,780
Comel, tapi…

161
00:11:11,449 --> 00:11:12,825
agak bising.

162
00:11:13,909 --> 00:11:16,412
Lain kali bawa saya jumpa anjing itu juga.

163
00:11:17,830 --> 00:11:18,706
Okey.

164
00:11:23,127 --> 00:11:25,379
Sol-i.

165
00:11:26,922 --> 00:11:28,090
Sol-i.

166
00:11:29,633 --> 00:11:30,676
Ayah!

167
00:11:31,552 --> 00:11:34,638
Ke mana ayah pergi? Saya sangat risau.

168
00:11:34,722 --> 00:11:36,223
Saya sedang bermimpikah?

169
00:11:37,933 --> 00:11:38,893
Tak.

170
00:11:38,976 --> 00:11:40,603
Kalau ini mimpi, bangunlah cepat.

171
00:11:40,686 --> 00:11:42,480
Mak.

172
00:11:42,563 --> 00:11:43,814
Mak balik bersama ayah?

173
00:11:43,898 --> 00:11:47,318
Kami ke Pohang kerana hal kedai.

174
00:11:47,401 --> 00:11:52,239
Tapi mak dan ayah dah berbaik semula?

175
00:11:52,323 --> 00:11:55,618
Apa kamu merepek ini?

176
00:11:55,701 --> 00:11:58,871
Tak ada pasangan yang
lebih bahagia daripada kami.

177
00:11:58,954 --> 00:12:01,081
- Sayang!
- Aduhai.

178
00:12:01,165 --> 00:12:02,958
Keluarlah. Mak masak ketam.

179
00:12:03,042 --> 00:12:05,336
Itu makanan kegemaran kamu berdua.

180
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:07,296
Keluar cepat.

181
00:12:07,379 --> 00:12:09,632
Memang betul. Saya suka.

182
00:12:09,715 --> 00:12:10,549
Mak!

183
00:12:25,314 --> 00:12:27,274
UJI BAKAT KEDUA <i>KOREA SINGS</i>
BANDAR OSAN

184
00:12:27,358 --> 00:12:28,400
JOM DEBUT! JIN-HWAN KACAK!

185
00:12:31,904 --> 00:12:35,866
<i>Jadikanmu milikku</i>

186
00:12:35,950 --> 00:12:38,452
<i>Adalah impian yang terbuku di hati</i>

187
00:12:38,994 --> 00:12:44,708
<i>Aku akan pastikannya
Tak kira apa yang melanda</i>

188
00:12:50,923 --> 00:12:52,132
<i>Impianku suatu masa dulu</i>

189
00:12:52,216 --> 00:12:54,009
<i>Ingin jadi presiden, pilihan bapa</i>

190
00:12:54,093 --> 00:12:56,762
<i>Teman turut berkongsi impian itu…</i>

191
00:12:56,845 --> 00:12:59,181
Terima kasih. Peserta seterusnya.

192
00:12:59,682 --> 00:13:02,518
Saya ada satu lagi lagu.
Biar saya cuba sekali lagi.

193
00:13:04,144 --> 00:13:06,897
<i>Cintailah diriku</i>

194
00:13:06,981 --> 00:13:09,525
<i>Jangan buatku menangis</i>

195
00:13:15,447 --> 00:13:16,323
Geramnya.

196
00:13:17,116 --> 00:13:19,159
Semua pengadil tadi rabun.

197
00:13:19,243 --> 00:13:20,995
Tergamak mereka gagalkan saya?

198
00:13:21,745 --> 00:13:24,164
Jangan risau.
Awak boleh cuba lagi di Suwon.

199
00:13:24,248 --> 00:13:27,167
Betul. Anggap saja
kita datang untuk berkelah.

200
00:13:27,251 --> 00:13:29,920
Alang-alang dah datang,
apa kata kita bermalam di sini?

201
00:13:30,504 --> 00:13:33,340
Hei, awak cuma nak
habiskan masa dengan Heon, bukan?

202
00:13:34,008 --> 00:13:36,510
Hei! Apa salahnya?

203
00:13:36,594 --> 00:13:39,722
Betul, kita boleh bermalam dekat sini.
Nak tak?

204
00:13:39,805 --> 00:13:42,808
Saya kena balik. Mak saya akan risau.

205
00:13:42,891 --> 00:13:45,978
Ha-young, bukan selalu
kita dapat buat begini.

206
00:13:46,061 --> 00:13:47,646
Kita putuskan dengan undian.

207
00:13:48,981 --> 00:13:50,566
- Saya setuju.
- Saya juga.

208
00:13:50,649 --> 00:13:51,859
Saya juga.

209
00:14:00,367 --> 00:14:02,953
Kita perlu cari tempat bermalam dulu.

210
00:14:04,538 --> 00:14:07,166
Apa kata kita ke sana?

211
00:14:09,710 --> 00:14:10,878
- Terima kasih.
- Terima kasih.

212
00:14:10,961 --> 00:14:12,880
- Selamat malam.
- Baiklah.

213
00:14:14,381 --> 00:14:17,301
Awak tak rasa
kita patut hubungi keluarga kita?

214
00:14:17,885 --> 00:14:19,845
Betul. Mari hubungi mereka.

215
00:14:23,390 --> 00:14:24,391
- Mak.
- Mak.

216
00:14:24,475 --> 00:14:26,018
Saya bermalam di rumah Sol-i.

217
00:14:26,101 --> 00:14:29,104
Ha-young ingin bantu saya buat ulang kaji.

218
00:14:29,188 --> 00:14:30,856
- Sol-i?
- Ha-young?

219
00:14:32,608 --> 00:14:33,859
- Mak cik.
- Mak cik.

220
00:14:33,943 --> 00:14:35,319
Kami akan tidur awal.

221
00:14:35,402 --> 00:14:36,946
Kami akan tidur lepas itu.

222
00:14:37,029 --> 00:14:38,364
Jangan risau.

223
00:14:38,447 --> 00:14:40,199
Baiklah. Selamat malam.

224
00:14:41,617 --> 00:14:44,411
- Mak, selamat malam.
- Terima kasih, mak.

225
00:14:46,872 --> 00:14:47,748
Selesai.

226
00:14:48,332 --> 00:14:49,667
Helo?

227
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,460
Mak, saya bermalam di rumah kawan.

228
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:55,506
Bolehlah.

229
00:14:55,589 --> 00:14:56,924
Sekali saja.

230
00:15:04,765 --> 00:15:07,810
Helo, mak cik.
Saya Cha Heon, kawan Jin-hwan.

231
00:15:09,561 --> 00:15:10,688
Ya.

232
00:15:12,606 --> 00:15:14,650
Terima kasih. Baiklah.

233
00:15:15,734 --> 00:15:17,152
Okey?

234
00:15:26,787 --> 00:15:28,330
JURULATIH

235
00:15:30,749 --> 00:15:32,418
- Helo?
<i>- Woo Dae-sung</i>!

236
00:15:33,168 --> 00:15:35,587
<i>Seharian kamu tak berlatih. Kamu ke mana?</i>

237
00:15:37,589 --> 00:15:39,800
Saya di rumah kawan saya.

238
00:15:40,384 --> 00:15:43,595
<i>Apa? Ayah nak bercakap
dengan ayah kawan kamu itu, cepat!</i>

239
00:15:45,055 --> 00:15:46,181
Cepatlah.

240
00:15:55,649 --> 00:15:56,483
Helo.

241
00:15:56,567 --> 00:15:59,403
Saya ayah Jin-hwan.

242
00:15:59,486 --> 00:16:01,071
<i>Berhenti bergurau!</i>

243
00:16:01,155 --> 00:16:02,698
<i>Di mana orang tua awak?</i>

244
00:16:05,075 --> 00:16:06,368
Hei!

245
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:08,996
Maaf.

246
00:16:09,079 --> 00:16:11,373
Eloklah awak tak jawab telefon hari ini.

247
00:16:14,877 --> 00:16:17,463
Nahaslah saya apabila saya pulang nanti.

248
00:16:20,257 --> 00:16:21,550
Terima kasih.

249
00:16:22,551 --> 00:16:24,970
Banyaknya bintang.

250
00:16:25,596 --> 00:16:27,431
Betul. Cantiknya.

251
00:16:28,432 --> 00:16:30,851
Kerana tekun belajar, kita cuma tunduk

252
00:16:30,934 --> 00:16:32,895
dan tak perasaan
langit yang begitu cantik.

253
00:16:34,146 --> 00:16:35,022
Hei, Jin-hwan.

254
00:16:35,856 --> 00:16:37,858
Sejak bila awak belajar dengan tekun?

255
00:16:37,941 --> 00:16:39,485
Awak sibuk tersengguk tidur.

256
00:16:39,568 --> 00:16:42,821
Saat ini amat menyentuh perasaan.
Awak patut senyap.

257
00:16:42,905 --> 00:16:44,740
Kamu berdua patut senyap.

258
00:16:45,449 --> 00:16:47,951
Walaupun semua bintang nampak sama,

259
00:16:48,035 --> 00:16:51,163
tapi ia terbahagi kepada
planet dan satelit.

260
00:16:51,789 --> 00:16:54,666
Adakah <i>Rosetta</i>
dan <i>Philae</i> juga ada di sana?

261
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:57,711
<i>Rosetta</i> dan <i>Philae</i>? Apa itu?

262
00:16:57,795 --> 00:17:01,882
Pada tahun 2004, sebuah pesawat
bernama <i>Rosetta</i> dilancarkan ke angkasa.

263
00:17:02,674 --> 00:17:06,220
Ia dilancarkan bersama
sebuah pendarat robotik bernama <i>Philae.</i>

264
00:17:07,513 --> 00:17:09,223
Kamu semua masih mendengar?

265
00:17:15,604 --> 00:17:18,190
Walaupun <i>Philae</i> berjaya mendarat,

266
00:17:18,273 --> 00:17:20,484
tapi ia terputus hubungan dengan <i>Rosetta</i>.

267
00:17:21,777 --> 00:17:24,696
Tahi bintang! Kita patut buat hajat!

268
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:27,741
Tahi bintang? Saya patut buat hajat!

269
00:17:30,494 --> 00:17:31,912
Saya bercakap sendirian?

270
00:17:36,875 --> 00:17:38,585
Awak tak ada hajat?

271
00:17:38,669 --> 00:17:40,420
Ia cuma sekumpulan batu dan habuk.

272
00:17:41,672 --> 00:17:44,174
Jadi ia tak boleh dengar hajat awak.

273
00:17:57,354 --> 00:18:00,357
Macam mana dengan
mak dan ayah awak? Dah okey?

274
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,692
Ya.

275
00:18:02,276 --> 00:18:05,070
Mereka sehati sejiwa,
jadi mereka bergaduh tak lama.

276
00:18:05,154 --> 00:18:06,905
Baguslah kalau begitu.

277
00:18:07,948 --> 00:18:11,493
Tapi terima kasih kerana sudi mendengar.

278
00:18:12,619 --> 00:18:16,123
Oh, ya. Betulkah awak tak buat hajat tadi?

279
00:18:17,916 --> 00:18:21,003
Betul. Apa hajat awak?

280
00:18:21,086 --> 00:18:22,004
Saya?

281
00:18:24,006 --> 00:18:25,007
Saya berdoa…

282
00:18:26,508 --> 00:18:27,801
supaya awak suka saya.

283
00:18:29,678 --> 00:18:31,638
Tapi saya dah tarik balik.

284
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:36,768
- Kenapa?
- Apa maksud awak?

285
00:18:36,852 --> 00:18:38,395
Ia menyedihkan.

286
00:18:39,646 --> 00:18:42,274
Menaruh harapan sedangkan saya tahu

287
00:18:42,357 --> 00:18:44,234
saya bertepuk sebelah tangan.

288
00:18:44,318 --> 00:18:48,197
Saya nak keadaan kekal seperti sekarang.

289
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:50,365
Nanti saya boleh terus sukakan awak.

290
00:18:51,742 --> 00:18:53,076
Oh, ya.

291
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:57,456
Katalah satu hari nanti
saya begitu marah kepada awak

292
00:18:57,539 --> 00:19:00,709
dan jika saya cakap begini,
"Hei, Cha Heon,

293
00:19:00,792 --> 00:19:02,711
saya takkan suka awak lagi",

294
00:19:03,921 --> 00:19:05,339
jangan cakap apa-apa.

295
00:19:05,422 --> 00:19:06,340
Apa?

296
00:19:06,840 --> 00:19:09,635
Sebab saya tak maksudkan. Okey?

297
00:19:18,435 --> 00:19:21,855
Awak nak main Permainan Cakap Benar?

298
00:19:21,939 --> 00:19:24,816
Tentu seronok. Tulislah cepat.

299
00:20:03,772 --> 00:20:06,358
<i>Semoga </i>Rosetta <i>dan </i>Philae <i>bahagia.</i>

300
00:20:07,526 --> 00:20:10,570
<i>Saya suka orang dengan
rambut paling panjang di sini.</i>

301
00:20:11,071 --> 00:20:13,657
SAYA SUKA SHIN SOL-I

302
00:20:23,583 --> 00:20:26,211
Simpan rahsia ini. Jangan dedahkan.

303
00:20:26,295 --> 00:20:27,671
- Okey.
- Okey.

304
00:20:51,278 --> 00:20:53,363
Macam mana? Menakjubkan, bukan?

305
00:20:54,823 --> 00:20:56,742
Betul. Cantiknya.

306
00:21:05,417 --> 00:21:06,960
Tak bergema.

307
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:12,382
Tapi cubalah. Giliran awak pula.

308
00:21:12,924 --> 00:21:13,967
Saya?

309
00:21:16,428 --> 00:21:19,348
Jeong Jin-hwan bodoh!

310
00:21:20,807 --> 00:21:21,683
Awak pula.

311
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:31,943
Kawan-kawan, saksikan saya
menang pingat emas minggu depan!

312
00:21:32,736 --> 00:21:34,780
Okey. Giliran awak pula, kawan.

313
00:21:37,157 --> 00:21:41,036
Saya harap Heon akan cakap sesuatu!

314
00:21:50,712 --> 00:21:52,464
Park Ji-sung, selamat berjaya!

315
00:21:55,425 --> 00:21:57,719
Apa ini? Dia betul-betul buat.

316
00:21:59,846 --> 00:22:02,933
Heon, awak tak sihat?

317
00:22:11,358 --> 00:22:13,777
Seronoknya!

318
00:22:13,860 --> 00:22:16,154
- Seronoknya!
- Seronoknya!

319
00:22:17,072 --> 00:22:18,281
Seronoknya!

320
00:22:18,365 --> 00:22:22,911
Saya paling suka Ha-young!

321
00:22:42,347 --> 00:22:45,225
Awak tulis apa
ketika Permainan Cakap Benar itu?

322
00:22:45,308 --> 00:22:47,185
<i>Tahu tak Sabtu ini hari jadi Sol-i?</i>

323
00:22:47,269 --> 00:22:49,271
Sol-i, hai.

324
00:22:49,354 --> 00:22:50,272
{\an8}Awak sibuk esok?

325
00:22:50,355 --> 00:22:52,566
Sol-i, apa menu esok?

326
00:22:52,649 --> 00:22:54,359
<i>Awak di mana? Saya ke sana.</i>

327
00:22:54,442 --> 00:22:57,904
<i>- Tentang nota Permainan Cakap Benar itu.
- Itu rahsia.</i>

328
00:22:57,988 --> 00:22:59,656
<i>Awak bercakap benar, bukan?</i>

329
00:22:59,739 --> 00:23:00,866
Semuanya kerana dia.

330
00:23:00,949 --> 00:23:03,785
<i>Awak ingin umumkan
yang awak ada teman wanita?</i>

331
00:23:03,869 --> 00:23:05,203
<i>Nah. Jangan ikut saya.</i>

332
00:23:05,287 --> 00:23:07,664
Saya takkan datang Sabtu nanti.
Jangan tunggu.

333
00:23:10,542 --> 00:23:15,547
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazizah Ali

